comment0.target=UrRobot
comment0.text=\n\ A\ UrRobot\ can\ carry\ out\ the\ five\ basic\ operations\:\ move,\ turnLeft,\n\ pickBeeper,\ putBeeper,\ and\ turnOff.\ Extend\ this\ class\ to\ solve\ some\n\ interesting\ problems.\n\ \n\ @author\ Joseph\ Bergin\n\ @version\ 1.0\ (Greenfoot)\ January\ 2010\n
